Make these cahnges to run in prod from locally running the project.

1. Remove the proxy from package.json file of client - "proxy": "http://localhost:8000"
2. Comment the RemoveUriSuffixMiddleware function in app.js file in server.
3. Change the .gitignore in main/master branch to 
    Docs
    docker-compose-dev.yml
    docker-compose-prod.yml
    docker-compose.yml